        authenticityMarker: "Castroville, self-proclaimed Artichoke Capital of the World, has grown Globe artichokes in the cool marine air of the Salinas Valley approach since the 1920s; the baby artichoke variety available here has no inner choke to remove, making the entire vegetable edible and the fried preparation possible — this is not feasible with artichokes grown in any other region of the country."
